---
title: Chermoula Coconut Lentil & Veggie Soup with Flatbreads & Almonds
description: Let’s soup-up this Middle Eastern version of a lentil soup! Mild spices bring a zap to the coconut and tomato base, while roasted veggies stirred through help to bulk it out. Serve up with a side of flatbreads for dipping, and there you have it - a powerhouse soup that will be loved by everyone.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
